              "widgetType": "text-editor",
              "settings": {
                "editor": "<p style='font-family:Raleway,sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.8;color:#888888;text-align:center;margin:16px auto 0;max-width:520px;'>A plain-English outline of every service and workshop on offer — session types, what's included, how pricing works, and how to book. Designed to be saved, shared, and referred back to.</p><ul style='font-family:Raleway,sans-serif;font-size:14px;color:#888;line-height:2;list-style:none;padding:20px 0 0;text-align:center;margin:0;'><li>✦ Commercial sessions from £1,495</li><li>✦ Documentary storytelling commissions</li><li>✦ Corporate portrait &amp; headshot packages</li><li>✦ Half-day and full-day workshops (Brighton &amp; London)</li><li>✦ One-to-one mentorship</li><li>✦ Online webinars</li></ul>"
